wrong.

24:43.615 --> 24:46.852 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
My only thought was, I'm
innocent and everyone
needs to I know.

24:46.885 --> 24:50.622 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I didn't even think for a second
about her."

24:50.656 --> 24:56.328 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Also last week, the American
Film Institute
canceled a screening of the
