asking is why white Protestant
America has

40:07.272 --> 40:09.540 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
experienced such a dramatic
decline.

40:09.574 --> 40:11.342 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Why did you want to tackle that
question?

40:11.376 --> 40:13.111 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ROBERT JONES, Author, "The End
of White Christian
America": Well, thanks for
having me.

40:13.144 --> 40:19.217 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You know, when I was looking at
the data,
I realized that we had really
crossed this

40:19.250 --> 40:21.586 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
very significant threshold in
American culture.

40:21.619 --> 40:27.659 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that is that we had moved,
just in the
last eight years, from being a
majority white

40:27.692 --> 40:31.796 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Christian country, 54 percent in
2008, when
Barack Obama was running for
president the

40:31.829 --> 40:35.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
