and Christian.

40:39.270 --> 40:43.808 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now, when I use the term white
Christian America,
I am really referring to this
cultural and

40:43.841 --> 40:46.911 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
institutional world built
primarily by Protestants.

40:46.944 --> 40:52.183 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, if you think about the
cultural center
of the U.S. being a kind of
Waspy, white,

40:52.216 --> 40:55.687 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Anglo-Saxon, Protestant culture,
that's the
culture that I'm talking about
and that has

40:55.720 --> 40:57.722 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
really faded from the center of
American culture.

40:57.755 --> 41:01.659 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And you talk --
