are, you were
white, you were Protestant, and
you were male.

41:17.108 --> 41:20.845 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that really held sway all
the way up through
the latter part of the 20th
century.

41:20.878 --> 41:26.184 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And then what
started happening
in the -- you say roughly in the
'60s, 1970s

41:26.217 --> 41:28.119 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
