41:57.949 --> 42:01.986 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, that's the --
and that's
a change from previous
generations, that may

42:02.019 --> 42:08.326 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
