42:31.916 --> 42:33.651 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
has ever seen.

42:33.684 --> 42:35.620 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But, Robert
Jones, you also
write, of course, about the
birth rate being

42:35.653 --> 42:39.490 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
