42:39.524 --> 42:40.691 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ROBERT JONES: Yes, that's right.

42:40.725 --> 42:42.527 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
There is an internal factor.

42:42.560 --> 42:46.631 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
That is this kind of
disaffiliation, but the
