42:56.374 --> 42:58.176 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
ROBERT JONES: Yes.

42:58.209 --> 43:03.448 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Well, I think it's very
